org.osmdroid.tileprovider.modules

Interface IFilesystemCache

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SqliteArchiveTileWriter, SqlTileWriter, TileWriter

    public interface IFilesystemCache
    Represents a write-only interface into a file system cache.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      boolean exists(ITileSource pTileSourceInfo, MapTile pTile)
      return true if the map file for download already exists
      void onDetach()
      Used when the map engine is shutdown, use it to perform any clean up activities and to terminate any background threads
      boolean remove(ITileSource tileSource, MapTile tile)
      Removes a tile from the cache, see issue https://github.com/osmdroid/osmdroid/issues/426
      boolean saveFile(ITileSource pTileSourceInfo, MapTile pTile, InputStream pStream)
      Save an InputStream as the specified tile in the file system cache for the specified tile source.
